Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:06.04,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121747,126043}Maya had been going from one theatre\Nto another trying to get a job as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:126043,128670}One day Miss Tsukikage collapsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:12.63,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:128670,132633}but she was able to get medical care\Nthanks to help from Mr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:16.13,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:132633,136136}In the meantime, Maya's talent was\Nrecognized by Kikuko Harada of Eishin Za,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:20.09,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:136136,140097}and she obtained her first\Nrole in the performing arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:27.14,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141050,147147}{\an5\pos(766,730)\fscy95\blur1\fad(500,0)}—Episode 11—\NStage Storm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:27.14,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:140098,147147}East University Medical Center
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148357,149775}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149775,151610}It's called "A Woman's River".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151610,152194}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152194,154738}I play the role of Tazu,\Na babysitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.28,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:154738,156281}{\fad(0,500)}Screenplay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157616,161036}The heroine marries into\Na patriotic family in the Meiji era,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161036,165624}pursuing her true desires as a woman.\NIt's very dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166625,168126}Wow, that's a real woman's story!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168126,170253}Maya, are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170253,174049}Anyhow, seeing you go\Nto so many theatres,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174049,177177}you have a lot of guts\Nwhen it comes to acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178804,182599}Do your best, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182599,183767}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183767,186937}Your play at Eishin Za\Nwith Kikuko Harada
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186937,192067}will mean so much\Nto you as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192067,193360}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216298,219428}It has been such a long time,\NMiss Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220887,224599}Oh, how lovely to see you,\NMrs. Himekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224599,226309}You too, Miss Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226309,228270}You have grown into\Nsuch a beautiful lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230397,232107}I have heard about\Nyour involvement
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232107,234067}in "The Prince and the Pauper"\Nat Fujinaga Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234067,238572}Yes, I would like to try\Nmany different roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238572,244911}My daughter is one day hoping\Nto play the Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244911,246663}"The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246663,248123}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248123,252085}She has become one of my strongest\Nrivals, is that not wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252085,255922}There is another young lady\Nyou should be keeping an eye on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257090,259760}I have encountered\Nanother rival for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:23.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261720,263930}Another rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267100,268477}It can't be…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268477,275025}I have cast a girl named\NKitajima Maya from Tsukikage Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275025,276401}Kitajima Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282032,285202}My guess is that\NMiss Tsukikage wishes to see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285202,287579}her attempt to become\Nthe Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288371,290707}Attempt to become\Nthe Crimson Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290707,292584}"The Crimson Goddess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292584,295003}Mr. Masumi,\Nis there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295003,296963}No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296963,298089}Mr. Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310602,311812}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311812,314606}She's the candidate\Nfor the Crimson Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314606,316149}No, I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316149,317442}Not to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341466,344970}Sleep tight, and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345387,348431}Oh, babysitting is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348431,352978}Sleep tight, and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352978,356106}Sleep tight, and smile…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356106,357691}{\an8}Sleep tight, and smile…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356565,360402}I had doubts about her,\Nbut she's doing pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360402,360943}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:06.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362279,366032}Why in the world did\NMiss Harada choose her over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366032,369369}Just watch, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371079,372580}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375667,377252}Oh, Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377252,379212}I just thought I'd drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388054,389848}Your first day is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389848,390599}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390599,392976}I can't believe I get\Nto perform again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392976,395937}Practicing has felt\Nso good lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395937,397313}Sounds like you're\Nback to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397313,402819}You don't mind forgetting about theatre\Nfor a little and hanging out with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402819,403527}No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414831,416625}Get your T-shirts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416625,419586}Wow! I've never seen\Nanything like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419586,421922}Oh, crepes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421922,423048}I'll get one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423048,424174}What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424174,425342}Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452661,453745}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462337,464339}Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:48.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464339,468385}Why is Ayumi here\Nlooking like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478853,481147}She is an incredible genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:01.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481147,481940}So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483733,486361}To learn about a beggar's life\Nfor "The Prince and the Pauper"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486361,487487}But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488196,489823}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489823,492367}I refuse to let you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492367,494911}I have been called\Na genius my whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494911,497914}but I must prove\Nthat my talent outstrips yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497914,500709}You may be the candidate\Nfor the Crimson Goddess now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:25.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500709,505880}but I will prove to Miss Tsukikage\Nthat I am a more deserving actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523857,525775}Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528862,530989}So, that really was her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530989,534826}Yeah, I heard she goes everywhere\Nlooking and acting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534826,537370}The theatre members\Nare all pretty shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537370,542292}I guess she's unsatisfied with just being\Ntalented, now she's getting more experience
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542292,545545}so that someday she can play\Nthe Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545545,546671}The Crimson Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550175,550967}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550967,552593}Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552844,555847}Ayumi hopes to play\Nthe Crimson Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555847,557265}That genius, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561644,562728}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.44,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:564939,567442}{\fad(0,1500)}Fujinaga Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.86,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:567442,570862}{\fad(1500,0)}"The Prince and the Pauper"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576910,581414}There are so many kids.\NMust be summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581414,586711}Many kids love\NAyumi for her beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586711,591757}I'm a little worried about how\Neveryone will receive her new look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611861,614363}Oh, I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615657,617575}That's Himekawa Ayumi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617575,620286}No… No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625500,627794}Where's the money\Nyou got today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627794,629129}It's you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629129,630004}I got nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630004,631214}Watch how you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631214,633341}No dinner for you today, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634926,637470}Mom, I don't like that Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637470,638471}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638471,639889}Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641391,643601}So it was a mistake, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643935,646146}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649023,651151}I've had it. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658658,662453}I hear ya, old man.\NI'll go make some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666040,668626}Excuse me, Mr. and Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668626,670795}Please have mercy\Nand spare some change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670795,671629}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671629,675175}Excuse me, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675175,677593}Nice ta meetcha,\Nthe name's Tom Canty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679053,680972}Look at that candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680972,683850}It looks so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683850,685810}You really givin' that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686769,688897}Thank ya so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695570,699741}What is she doing going around\Nthe audience like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699741,702285}But the audience's attitude\Nhas completely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710543,713504}"The Prince and the Pauper"\Nhad an excellent first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713504,716799}"The genius Himekawa Ayumi\Nproved her talent."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716799,719427}"Playing two roles in one play"…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719427,720762}Such good reviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731439,733524}Today is my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733524,736361}I'll do it my own way,\Nand I'll do my best.
Comment: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:18.69,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:738695,738695}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:22.49,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:742492,742492}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:25.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:745453,745453}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:29.49,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:745745,749498}{\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&\t(0,1000,\1c&HE4F0CB&\3c&H24320A&\4c&H202020&)\fad(0,500)}Eishin Za
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.66,0:12:31.37,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:748665,751376}{\fad(500,500)}"A Woman's River"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754671,757090}Wow, all adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757090,759509}Mostly old men\Nand women, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760385,761803}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761803,763096}Miss Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763096,767183}Audiences can be very different,\Ndepending on the theatre or the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768059,772480}You will find they react very differently,\Neven if your acting remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772480,776109}What type of audiences\Nhave you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776609,777986}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777986,781072}Mostly students\Nand younger people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781072,782240}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782240,784117}Then it will be\Na good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784117,789414}We will see how what the audience\Nof Eishin Za thinks of your acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:13.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789414,793334}The atmosphere is really different\Nfrom what I'm used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796546,799173}What am I, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799173,802260}As his wife,\NI'm just a tool to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802260,804595}A tool to raise a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804595,807015}What's the reason\Nfor me to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809099,810059}I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810059,812562}Can my acting be accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813021,815189}H-Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817150,818401}This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819319,820486}You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822113,823364}It's my scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831122,832873}I'm Tazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842216,843176}Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843176,845386}The babysitter is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845386,847347}Her name is Tazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847347,849390}Hey, Tazu, greet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849390,850266}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851976,853394}I'm Tazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853394,856773}Your house is so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856773,860776}I heard it's best to babysit\Nat a rich house, but it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860776,867367}A village chief told me I can get\Nthree cups of white rice, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875875,878211}Now, Tazu, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879379,881172}Here, Tazu, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881172,882131}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888512,890055}Now then, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890055,893309}The reason I called you was…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:59.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897688,899399}The audience is looking at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899399,901901}She has stolen all the attention\Nfrom us, the lead roles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906364,908574}W-Why is everyone\Nlaughing so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908574,910660}What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910660,912161}She stands out so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912161,916499}She's just a normal girl, but when\Nshe's on stage, she really stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916499,918751}Her acting isn't\Nall that great, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:24.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922045,924674}Kitajima Maya.\NDon't think you're on top of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:27.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924674,927385}I'll make it so you won't be able\Nto stand on stage ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935601,937186}Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937186,941774}You can only stay for thirty minutes\Nif you want to make the next meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941774,943483}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948823,950616}What? There's no doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950616,952785}I just saw it right there,\Nbut now it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952785,953786}Can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953786,957540}She can't get on stage\Nif there's no doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962044,963588}Here! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963588,965256}It was sitting in the back room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965798,966674}Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967300,970428}How strange,\NI was sure I saw it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970428,972180}Here, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972180,973556}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973556,975183}Babysitter, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975183,975849}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977767,982273}Sleep tight, little baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982273,983900}Oh, that's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983900,985067}Yeah, that's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985693,991532}Sleep tight, little baby…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991532,995411}Oh, baby-sitting is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995411,1000208}They work me so hard,\Nand I only get one cup of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001375,1004003}That village chief\Nwas a big liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004003,1008341}Here, don't cry. The crows\Nwill laugh at you if you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008341,1010927}Sleep tight…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012470,1014931}little baby…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015306,1016390}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040164,1042083}Theatre is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:24.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042083,1044752}Go ahead and cry,\Nyou'll never get on stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047629,1049005}Miss Harada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077702,1080621}You sit back there\Nlike I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080621,1083624}Oh, it ain't easy\Nbabysitting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092758,1095511}No way!?\NI can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:19.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096345,1099432}Wonderful theatre spirit,\Nlittle girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099974,1101851}The future Crimson Goddess…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101851,1104395}She sure is something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105771,1109525}Okay, that's enough babysitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109525,1111360}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112987,1116949}Sleep tight…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116949,1119452}little baby…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119452,1122288}Sleep tight…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:52.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129378,1132214}I thought I would die…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137720,1139263}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:01.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139263,1141932}Now people think\Neven more highly of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:10.56,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1144935,1150566}Fujinaga Hall\N"The Prince and the Pauper"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151233,1153653}It's as popular as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153653,1155738}Tickets are sold out every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155738,1160034}Ms. Ayumi will monopolize\Nall the tabloid news for this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.99,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1160034,1162995}{\an2}Everything You Need to Know\NAbout the Girl Genius, Himekawa Ayumi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163245,1167333}But she must be out of her mind\Nto aim for "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167333,1168417}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168417,1171587}The play rights\Nare Miss Tsukikage's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171587,1174674}There's no way she will let\NAyumi from Ondine play the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174674,1175466}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175466,1177885}Miss Tsukikage\Nis only looking for talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186310,1190189}If Miss Tsukikage\Nrecognizes Ayumi's talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190189,1192983}she will consider her for\N"The Crimson Goddess", too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192983,1194735}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199240,1201117}I'm Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201117,1202868}I'm not Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202868,1206455}I keep telling you, I'm Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206455,1208457}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208457,1210710}Let me go.\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210710,1213546}Let me go!\NLet me go—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218759,1219677}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.38,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1222138,1224389}{\fad(0,1000)}Eishin Za
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.10,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1224389,1227101}{\fad(1500,0)}"A Woman's River"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227393,1229687}Wow, I get chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229687,1233983}I don't know\Nif I can be your little cupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234692,1239113}Don't you think she gets more and more\Nof the audience's attention every minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239113,1242032}Yes, have you noticed\Nthe audience's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242032,1244910}They've all turned away from Shino,\Nand they're looking at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247163,1252293}If she had a bigger role,\Nshe would have easily overtaken us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:59.59,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1256380,1259592}Maya was doing great\Non the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:04.13,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1259592,1264138}For some reason though,\NMiss Harada's strict gaze did not soften.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265473,1268392}What's that girl's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268392,1270101}Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273564,1275691}She's not on the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275691,1277777}Then look her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277777,1280738}She's pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280737,1284074}We might want her\Nfor our theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284909,1286118}Miss Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286118,1288287}She's pretty good, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288287,1292166}Would you like her\Nfor our next play?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292166,1293082}Miss Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295044,1296504}No…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296504,1299340}This will be her last role.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299340,1300381}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300381,1301467}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301467,1305262}You were the one\Nwho wanted to use her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305262,1310893}She could be a huge risk.\NIt all depends on how you cast her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310893,1313437}Especially here at Eishin Za.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313437,1315856}W-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320402,1323489}She has an incredible fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329578,1332832}Yes, a fate called Stage Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334458,1336836}Stage Storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342633,1347012}Please tell me, Ms. Harada,\Nwhat do you mean by Stage Storm?
